Samajh gaya. Yeh tasveer (picture) bohot professional hai aur portfolio ke "Hero Section" (sabse upar wala hissa) mein lagne ke liye perfect hai.

Aapne "Demo" manga hai, toh pehle main aapko batata hoon ke yeh code add karne ke baad kaisa dikhega, aur phir main aapko poora code doonga.

-----

### üåü Demo: Kaisa Dikhega?

Hum is tasveer ko "Creative aur Professional" banane ke liye yeh changes karenge:

1.  **Shape:** Tasveer ko ek perfect **Circle (Gola)** mein kaatenge. Yeh modern portfolio ka standard design hai.
2.  **Border & Glow:** Us circle ke gard aapki website ki theme color (Professional Blue) ka ek border aur halka sa **creative glow** (chamak) hoga.
3.  **Layout:**
      * **Laptop/PC par:** Aapki tasveer left side par hogi, aur aapka naam/intro right side par likha hoga. Yeh bohot balanced aur professional lagta hai.
      * **Mobile par:** Tasveer upar center mein hogi, aur text uske neeche aayega.
4.  **Animation:** Jab koi mouse tasveer ke upar le kar jayega, toh woh halki si zoom hogi (hover effect).

-----

### ‚úÖ Step 1: Tasveer ko Save Karein (Sabse Zaroori)

Code chalane se pehle aapko yeh karna hoga:

1.  Jo tasveer aapne bheji hai, usko apne computer mein **ussi folder** mein save karein jahan aapki `index.html` file hai.
2.  Tasveer ka naam change kar ke **`profile.png`** rakh dein. (Naam exactly yehi hona chahiye).

-----

### ‚úÖ Step 2: Updated Final Code

Neeche poora naya code hai. Is mein maine CSS mein changes kiye hain taake tasveer professional lage, aur HTML mein tasveer add ki hai.

Apni purani `index.html` ka saara code delete karein aur yeh naya wala paste kar dein.

